  "body": "I'm interested in a `--keystore` flag that takes a path to a `/keystore` directory not relative to the `datadir`. I'd like to put my `/keystore` on a removable encrypted drive while still being able to mount and quickly do account operations with `geth --keystore /path/to/mounted/keystore`. Thoughts? Does a better pattern already exist for this?\n",
